<p>Loved-up: Hailey shared a cute photo of the married couple embracing on a boat, as well as a shot that showed off her trim physique and her black bikini</p>

<p>On Friday, Justin shared a cryptic blue-tinted photo of himself in a striped shirt and shorts.</p>

<p>The Let Me Love You Singer simply captioned it, '1 week,' which has left his fans wondering if he might be preparing to release new music.</p>

<p>Back in February, he released his fifth studio album Changes, which had been led by the underwhelming single Yummy.</p>

<p>The album debuted atop the charts, though it received middling reviews from critics. </p>

<p>Coming soon? On Friday, Justin shared a cryptic photo captioned, '1 week,' which some fans have speculated means he's about to release more music</p>
